data.title: Kubhinde, Khotang
data.meta_description: Kubhinde is a village and Village Development Committee in Khotang District in the Sagarmatha Zone of eastern Nepal. At the time of the 1991 Nepal census it had a population of 2,189 persons living in 406 individual households.
data.text:
Kubhinde is a village and Village Development Committee in Khotang District in the Sagarmatha Zone of eastern Nepal. At the time of the 1991 Nepal census it had a population of 2,189 persons living in 406 individual households.[1]
